creator: Various
description:
LibriVox recording of Compilation de poèmes - 005 by Various.
Read in French by millianna; Ezwa; Malone; Françoise; Philippe; Violette; Kasper; Pamela Nagami; BeniaminoMassimo; Andree-Ann Granger; Zeckou

Cette compilation comprend une série de poèmes lus, en langue française, pour LibriVox. (Ezwa)

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
